sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as AgentRuntime Controller<br/>kagenti-system
    participant Webhook as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Deployment as Target Deployment
    participant Pod as Agent Pod
    participant AuthBridge as AuthBridge Sidecar<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant SPIRE as SPIRE Workload API<br/>Unix Socket gRPC mTLS
    participant Keycloak as Keycloak<br/>8080/443 TCP
    participant BundleSvc as Bundle Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant AgentApp as Agent Container<br/>localhost

    Note over User,AgentApp: Flow 1: Agent Enrollment via AgentRuntime

    User->>K8sAPI: POST AgentRuntime CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (informer)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment labels + config hash<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Deployment: Rolling update triggered
    Deployment->>K8sAPI: Create Pod
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: AdmissionReview (POST)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / API server cert
    Webhook->>Webhook: Inject AuthBridge sidecar<br/>+ init container + env vars
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod spec
    K8sAPI->>Pod: Schedule pod with sidecar

    Note over User,AgentApp: Flow 2: Agent Card Verification (mTLS Verified Fetch)

    participant CardCtrl as AgentCard Controller
    participant AgentSvc as Agent Service<br/>8443/TCP mTLS

    User->>K8sAPI: POST AgentCard CR
    K8sAPI->>CardCtrl: Watch event
    CardCtrl->>SPIRE: Request X.509 SVID<br/>Unix socket / mTLS
    SPIRE-->>CardCtrl: X.509 SVID + trust bundle
    CardCtrl->>AgentSvc: GET /.well-known/agent.json<br/>8443/TCP mTLS (SPIFFE)
    AgentSvc-->>CardCtrl: A2A Agent Card (JSON)
    CardCtrl->>CardCtrl: Verify JWS signature<br/>against SPIRE trust bundle
    CardCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Update NetworkPolicy<br/>based on verification result

    Note over User,AgentApp: Flow 3: AuthBridge Inbound Request Pipeline

    participant Client as External Client

    Client->>AuthBridge: Request to agent<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    AuthBridge->>Keycloak: Fetch JWKS / validate JWT<br/>HTTPS/443 or HTTP/8080
    Keycloak-->>AuthBridge: Token validation result
    AuthBridge->>BundleSvc: Fetch OPA policy bundle<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    BundleSvc-->>AuthBridge: Rego policy bundle
    AuthBridge->>AuthBridge: Evaluate OPA policy<br/>(ibac plugin)
    AuthBridge->>AgentApp: Forward request<br/>localhost / plaintext
    AgentApp-->>AuthBridge: Response
    AuthBridge-->>Client: Response
